29231.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
29231.description: The gang goes to the theater to see a play about themselves, but are not happy with the production and the inaccurate portrayals of themselves.

29232.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
29232.description: Aang finds out that Ozai plans to burn down the Earth Kingdom with an airship fleet. He disappears during the night, having sleepwalked onto a mysterious moving island. His friends cannot find him, and go to June for help. Meanwhile, Ozai is crowned Phoenix King.

29233.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29233.description: SpongeBob's new friend is a giant fluffy hamster. There's one problem, though: no one else can see him! // Patrick wants to be a horse!

29234.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29234.description: Gary has a pet translation collar, and he's talking up a storm. Everyone loves it... except for Squidward! // When a small clown gets left behind by the circus, SpongeBob takes the hapless harlequin under his wing.

29235.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29235.description: Casey Jones thinks he can take on the criminal underworld on his own, but he soon finds himself in over his head.

29236.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29236.description: A new mutant called Muckman starts to gain notoriety as NYC's "Monster Hero".

29237.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29237.description: It's a battle between master and father when Shifu and Mr. Ping compete for Po's attention and affection during a camping trip. But will their competition get in the way of Po defeating the Valley's newest menace?

29238.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29238.description: After a blow to the head leaves Po with amnesia, Fung and the Croc Bandits are more than happy to use it to their advantage...by convincing the Dragon Warrior that he is their evil bandit leader.

29239.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29239.description: The Space Agency intends to send one of the chimps to the moon. In the opinion of certain flightless waterfowl, this important mission would be much better served by sending a flightless waterfowl instead. Private proves to be best suited for the trip (believe it or not) and with the help of a clever monkey suit disguise, he ends up on the moon.

29240.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29240.description: When a sneeze from Rico causes the underground tunnel system beneath the zoo to rupture Skipper calls in 4 beavers to fix the situation. // Skipper's having one of those perfect days, and he decides to use the opportunity to settle an old score.

29241.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29241.description: Plankton poses as a wish-granting genie in his latest scheme to get the secret formula. // Mr. Krabs' new Krabby soup is a hit - until some heat-loving hippies move into the soup vat!

29242.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29242.description: When Man Ray rents Squidward's house for the weekend, it's up to SpongeBob and Patrick to stop his evil vacation! // Mr. Krabs takes a vacation and makes Larry the Lobster the temporary manager of the Krusty Krab.

29243.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29243.description: Patrick leads an enthusiastic stranger on a tour of his favorite places in Bikini Bottom. // SpongeBob is afraid to get off the roof of the Krusty Krab, but he won't let that stop him from living his life!

29244.title: Nella The Princess Knight
29244.description: Nella and her friends get lost in Minatori's maze. // Miscommunication between Nella and Garrett causes their invention at the Royal Science Expo to go wrong.

29245.title: Nella The Princess Knight
29245.description: After Trinket's horn is bent in an accident, Nella helps her find a wise unicorn to fix it. // Nella and Trinket go on a quest to retrieve Trinket's childhood toy when she accidentally gives it away.

29246.title: Bubble Guppies
29246.description: Rawrrrrrr! While the Bubble Guppies are digging for dinosaur bones, they learn all about different types of dinosaurs.

29247.title: Bubble Guppies
29247.description: To celebrate Shrimptennial, the Bubble Guppies visit Big Bubble City! Join them in discovering the hustle and bustle of the big city and the Big Bubble Building!

29248.title: Dora the Explorer
29248.description: When young Pablo loses his magic flute, a terrible drought hits his family's farm. Dora and Boots find Pablo's flute, and hurry off to return it to Pablo on his Mountain.

29249.title: Dora the Explorer
29249.description: Dora and Boots keep running into friends in need of help. Turns out the other animals are all headed to a big party at the Treehouse. They beg Dora and Boots to come too!

29250.title: Rusty Rivets
29250.description: Rusty builds his Mom the ultimate relaxing chair, but whenever it hears any noise, it runs away and raises high into the sky! // Rusty, and Ruby try to save the Wake Up and Smell the Roses Contest from Frankie Fritz' stinky Robotic Skunk.

29251.title: Rusty Rivets
29251.description: When Liam gets trapped atop a tall stack of junk with his stuffed dinosaur, Rusty designs a Jurassic rescue. // When Mr. Higgins' remote control plane won't land, Rusty and the gang must bring it down safely - using Crush as a daredevil rescue pilot hero!

29252.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
29252.description: Crusher and Pickle challenge Blaze and his friends to a sailboat race. But when he tries to cheat, Crusher accidentally crashes both ships onto a tropical island! Blaze and his crew must find the missing pieces of their ship so they can sail home.

29253.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
29253.description: It’s the day of the Team Truck Challenge, a race where all the trucks get to compete in teams of two! But when Crusher chooses a new partner instead of Pickle, his disappointed sidekick teams up with Blaze to prove his mettle.

29254.title: PAW Patrol
29254.description: It’s Adventure Bay Race Day and the pups are about to race each other all across the town to see who is the fastest pup. One other competitor unexpectedly shows up though, Alex in his super trike! // Mr.Porter enters a cake competition and needs Ryder and the pups to help him bake the biggest and tastiest cake. The race is on to get their cake baked and to the competition on time!

29255.title: PAW Patrol
29255.description: Cap'n Turbot accidentally stumbles into a secret cavern that was once a pirate's hideout. When the PAW Patrol rescues him, they find an incomplete treasure map. The adventure is on to find the sunken pirate treasure!

29256.title: PAW Patrol
29256.description: Someone has been swiping fish off Cap’n Turbot’s boat, so he calls Ryder and the PAW Patrol to help investigate. Using his new SPY GEAR, Chase inspects the boat and heads below deck where he discovers it’s a group of pesky Penguins! Now the Pups have to catch the slippery suspects and find a way to get them back to the South Pole! // Adventure Bay’s newest Dolphin Pup accidentally swims into a shallow water stream! Now it’s up to Ryder and PAW Patrol to get her back into the Bay and with her parents.

29257.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29257.description: The night before the big school dance, Mr. Krabs asks SpongeBob to help Pearl get rid of a barnacle on her face. // SpongeBob asks Patrick to pet-sit Gary while he's away at his Grandma's birthday party.

29258.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29258.description: House Sittin’ for Sandy: SpongeBob house-sits for Sandy, and all is quiet until Patrick shows up. Smooth Jazz at Bikini Bottom: After losing their passes, SpongeBob and Squidward try to sneak backstage at the sold-out Kelpy G show.

29259.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29259.description: The Krabby Patty That Ate Bikini Bottom: Mr Krabs uses Sandy’s experimental growth formula on a Krabby Patty with disastrous results. Bubble Buddy Returns: SpongeBob tries to keep Bubble Buddy’s visiting son, Shiny, out of trouble and away from sharp edges.

29260.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29260.description: Kowalski's invention that stops time falls into the worst hands possible. King Julien's. The lemur promptly breaks it trapping the two of them in a world frozen in time. Instead of being a disaster, however, they realize they can do everything their hearts desire - invent like crazy, perform on Broadway, play tennis in the middle of the street. But even an infinite playland like this can't last forever! // Special Agent Buck Rockgut makes a "triumphant" return. While hunting the Red Squirrel across the globe, the crusty old bird contacts the penguins with a warning that the diabolical squirrel has a brainwashed sleeper agent among them. They battle each other to a standstill to uncover the agent - will it tear the unit apart? Can trust ever be restored? They have to take a trip to a faraway borough to uncover the truth.

29261.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29261.description: Dr. Blowhole, uber nemesis of the Penguins, returns to New York with a plan so diabolical it plays like a symphony of evil.

29262.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29262.description: Fung finds an old scroll with instructions for making living terra cotta warriors, and soon it's up to Po and the Five to stop his monstrous clay creation.

29263.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29263.description: When Po is possessed by the ghost of evil Master Ding, it's up to Tigress to save him before Ding can unleash his powers and enslave the Valley of Peace.

29264.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29264.description: The team comes to grips with the possibility that Leo won't get better, while things only get worse: a new mutant captures Raph!

29265.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29265.description: The Turtles discover Bigfoot in the woods, and Donnie befriends it, insisting they protect it from a hunter that is after it.

29266.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29266.description: While trying to wrestle open the cap off of a tube of toothpaste SpongeBob accidentally punches himself in the face leaving behind a hideous black eye. // Plankton has brainwashed Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy! With the dynamic duo under Plankton’s control, he orders them to wreak havoc on the Krusty Krab. It’s up to SpongeBob SquarePants and his trusty spatula to save the day!

29267.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29267.description: Instead of getting on the ship headed for summer camp, SpongeBob and Patrick accidentally board a ship full of prisoners on their way to jail on Inferno Island. // SpongeBob and Pat stow away on one of Sandy’s extreme wilderness expeditions. But when they get accidentally left behind, they must band together in order to survive in the wild.

29268.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29268.description: While researching his family tree SpongeBob discovers that he was related to the great Western hero, and famous chili-slinger, SpongeBuck.

29269.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29269.description: Tigress is forced to babysit a small child who has been separated from his parents.

29270.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29270.description: Po and Mantis visit the equivalent of an ancient Chinese Comic-Con, where Po's fanboy enthusiasm gets out of hand.

29271.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29271.description: When Doris the Dolphin shows up with Parker the Platypus and asks a favor of Kowalski, he instantly jumps to her rescue only to find out it’s to free her brother Francis who happens to be a “mind-jacked” Dr. Blowhole.

29272.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29272.description: Rico’s beloved doll, Miss Perky, has a new line of princess accessories! Joy! But in order for Skipper to reward the loco penguin with the new swag he must fill a marble jar (one marble in for good behavior, one marble out for bad.) How in the world is Rico supposed to behave and fill the jar when King Julien has kidnapped his dolly with the intention of marrying her?

29273.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29273.description: The Shredder kidnaps and experiments on the Mighty Mutanimals.

29274.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29274.description: Mikey and Casey are befriended by Mondo Gecko, a radical skateboarding reptilian kid.

29275.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29275.description: Mr. Krabs and Plankton woo customers with greasy entrees. // SpongeBob tries a career at being a model in a kitchen sponge commercial.

29276.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29276.description: Squidward cleans up the city of Bikini Bottom with "help" from SpongeBob. // SpongeBob brings Gary a pet that terrorizes him.

29277.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29277.description: SpongeBob and Patrick buy a toy and have to learn to share it. // SpongeBob goes with Mr. Krabs to the Cheapest Crab Convention.

29278.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29278.description: Po's visit to a famous war hero goes awry when he finds out the retired general is off his rocker.

29279.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29279.description: Po tries to help Crane get his 'mojo' back after Crane is humiliated at a charity event.

29280.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29280.description: When the Penguins lose access to their favorite snack, popcorn, Skipper and crew leap into action to gain a new supply of the salty treat. // When a camera falls from the sky into the lemur habitat, Julien and Maurice argue about who will keep the shiny toy. But when Maurice disappears in the struggle, the Penguins are called in to find the missing lemur.

29281.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29281.description: When the zoo installs web cams to bring in new visitors, Private accidentally becomes an Internet star. // Skipper accidentally causes King Julien to lose his beloved crown. The penguins go on a dangerous mission to retrieve the crown from the sewer.

29282.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
29282.description: The gang find Iroh with June's help. Iroh suggests that Zuko challenge Azula for the position of Fire Lord, with Katara to help. The others decide to intercept the airship fleet. Meanwhile, Aang comes to the conclusion that he must kill Ozai after talking to previous Avatars and finds out the island he was on was a Lion Turtle. The comet arrives at the end.

29283.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
29283.description: Sokka, Toph and Suki begin destroying the airship fleet. Aang duels Ozai, but is soon overwhelmed because of his reluctance to kill him. Zuko fights Azula in an Agni Kai, but is shot by lightning in the process of saving Katara from it.

29284.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29284.description: SpongeBob and Patrick disturb the Flying Dutchman's slumber and he turns them into ghosts. // Squidward and SpongeBob have to share a locker.

29285.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29285.description: SpongeBob and Patrick protest the construction of a highway that would destroy Jellyfish Fields.

29286.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29286.description: SpongeBob and Patrick go back in time to see the young Mermaidman and Barnacleboy. // SpongeBob and Patrick watch their heroes fight bad guys in a classic Mermaidman and Barnacleboy episode.

29287.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29287.description: Karai is brainwashed and starts hunting the Turtles.

29288.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29288.description: The Turtles get whisked through time by apprentice Time Master Renet, and they must all work together to defeat the evil Time Master Savanti Romero.

29289.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29289.description: When Shifu throws out his back, Po has to sit in as master of the Jade Palace.

29290.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29290.description: When kung fu is outlawed, Po turns to donning a mask to fight crime.

29291.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29291.description: Sick of Julien's annoying presence, the penguins decide to take a vacation on The Moon. // After Marlene is frightened by a spooky noise in the night, she and Skipper travel down to the sewer below the zoo to find the source of the scary moans.

29292.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29292.description: When stuffed Mort dolls become popular at the zoo, Julien gets jealous and get them recalled. Unfortunately, the real-life Mort is accidentally sent back to the factory along with his plush replicas. // Maurice bribes the zoo animals to celebrate “King Julien Day” by offering them candy. Only Skipper refuses to go along, but still he’s unable to avoid the annoying day.

29293.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29293.description: Marlene discovers a lost egg, and asks the penguins to care for it and keep it safe. But King Julien is jealous, and wants to raise the egg to be his second in command. // When Skipper steals the batteries to Julien’s stereo, he sets off a wild chase around the zoo that gets both of them stuck in the habitat of an angry kangaroo.

29294.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29294.description: Squidward bets SpongeBob he can't go a day without crying. // Mrs. Puff has to work through her summer break at the Krusty Krab.

29295.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29295.description: Mr. Krabs finds out that Plankton's afraid of whales. // Gary falls for a snail named Mary.

29296.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29296.description: Mr. Krab opens a Dinner Theater at the Krusty Krab. // SpongeBob takes his pals to Texas to see Sandy in a squirrel rodeo.
